---
title: Street-Cart-Style Chicken Shawarma Bowls with Bell Pepper, Pistachio Rice & Creamy Cilantro Sauce
description: Our chefs can’t get enough of the warming, aromatic flavors of shawarma. Here, chicken is marinated in shawarma spices and yogurt, then cooked until golden and tender. It’s piled into bowls with zesty, pistachio-studded basmati rice, sautéed bell pepper, and a creamy cilantro sauce for drizzling. It really doesn’t get much better than digging into all that.
